								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="posted-on"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> <a href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?p=1132" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-03-06T20:20:35+00:00">March 6, 2016</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-04-22T16:24:59+00:00">April 22, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?author=1">admin</a></span></span>
				
