						<div class="entry-content">

					<h2></h2>
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Painting with Mary for Kids</span></h2>
<div>
<div>
<div><strong>Saturday afternoons</strong></div>
<div><strong>2:00 p.m. to 4:00 p.m.</strong></div>
<div>For ages 6 to 10. Cost is $15.00 per 2-hour lesson. Space is limited. Pre-register at the library.</div>
<div>
<hr />
</div>
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Tot Time with Stacey</span></h2>
<div>
<div><strong>Thursday mornings, 10:30 am to 11:30 a.m.</strong></div>
<div><strong>January 14 to May 26, 2016</strong></div>
<div>Crafts, stories &amp; activities. For ages 2 to 4 with their parent/caregivers. Cost is $1.00 per session. Space is limited. Pre-register at the library.</p>
<hr />
</div>
