				<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?p=859" rel="bookmark">William Thomas Photo Collection on Loan to the Port Colborne Public Library</a></h1>

								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="posted-on"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> <a href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?p=859" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-04-15T13:50:09+00:00">April 15, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-03-01T15:22:20+00:00">March 1, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?author=1">admin</a></span></span>
				
				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
							</header><!-- .entry-header -->

						<div class="entry-content">

					<p>The Port Colborne Public Library is proud to announce that the library is the new home for writer William Thomas’ extraordinary collection of photographs from his “Readings at the Roselawn” author series. <a href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?p=859#more-859" class="more-link">(more&hellip;)</a></p>

				<p><a class="btn btn-default read-more" href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?p=859" title="William Thomas Photo Collection on Loan to the Port Colborne Public Library">Read More</a></p>

